Les employés doivent également être encouragés à utiliser strong, unique passwords für ihre accounts. 最後に, regelmäßige security training sessions können dazu beitragen, dass alle Mitarbeiter auf dem neuesten Stand der Sicherheitspraktiken bleiben.
translated_answer:
Phishing attacks are a cyberattack in which hackers attempt to steal confidential information. To protect a large company, it is essential to sensitize employees to recognize the signs of a phishing attempt. For example, suspicious emails with links or attachments should always be treated with caution.

However, implementing multi-factor authentication can help increase security. Employees should also be encouraged to use strong, unique passwords for your accounts. In other words, regular security training sessions can help ensure that all employees stay up to date with the latest security practices .
